{"tid":804510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯將帥不和又添一人？山齊士（山神）嬲爆被換出","createTime":"2018-09-03T05:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T14:19:36.000Z","uid":119778,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5cdf2ca860fea81197dbfed8f1cb9136e77e4fcb","tid":804510,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"曼聯作客般尼一仗中，山齊士傷癒復任正選，表現活躍。這位智利球員多次製造機會予盧卡古，更在上半場交出一記傳中球，盧卡古跳頂破網，為球隊先開紀錄。盧卡古在上半場梅開二度，領隊摩連奴見情況穩定，球隊亦有兩球領先優勢，在61分鐘收起剛傷癒的山齊士，盼給予他一點休息時間。不過，山齊士對被調離場並不太滿意，更在後備席廂怒掉繃帶洩忿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/132139_e8ed7347b5f22eee771980d0252ddaec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F132139_e8ed7347b5f22eee771980d0252ddaec.png&h=910dbfd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/132158_feade92260124c01fb95516f7a1dd3ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F132158_feade92260124c01fb95516f7a1dd3ab.png&h=aff60c62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/132217_7d3b1a1a5402b70c011bca923093118d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F132217_7d3b1a1a5402b70c011bca923093118d.png&h=c3ba8d83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/132239_0ff77535fed3b099d936ee2f9754b4a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F132239_0ff77535fed3b099d936ee2f9754b4a8.png&h=685ec4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/132258_f7b8d8045fb36c29a8a2ebc0bc74f6b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F132258_f7b8d8045fb36c29a8a2ebc0bc74f6b8.png&h=e1caec0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n摩連奴決定收起山齊士換入拉舒福特，山齊士被調離場後，先與主帥摩連奴及一眾職球員擊掌，並不見任何不悅之情。不過，山齊士坐在後備席廂時，解開在手上的繃帶，然後用力地掉在地上，狀甚不滿（另見置頂影片約1:56處）。後備入替的拉舒福特在上場不久後，更取得一面紅牌，未知當時在被調走的山齊士有何感覺。<br />\n<br />\n山齊士在賽後恭賀球隊獲勝，並沒有露出任何不悅之情"},{"pid":"fc1cbd306880334f9375055a9952f9b2d8c7e0b6","tid":804510,"uid":24121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acb9121df591fe5b35fb4ab30b988babfb37c494","tid":804510,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"佢份糧包埋受氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fcaed9f38027a1d549e499b83c74809efa207e","tid":804510,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"掉野啫咁就叫不滿， 扮型咋，牙朗都掉樽蓋紙啦"},{"pid":"ef46a461dd50b62b812d6911949107cce4c8d6aa","tid":804510,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:48:46.000Z","msg":"鬥心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c164e2265f31d7a408d9ec776fdb83cd2ac6e37c","tid":804510,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:49:03.000Z","msg":"看圖作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70eda1d6e26b721bbbc30704207f37393b5d54b8","tid":804510,"uid":6782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"佢似係埋怨自己狀態未夠好 佢好多次遠射起腳射中人"},{"pid":"0d7e143dad0ed2ceb58d60a20ad40bd3ec1e528c","tid":804510,"uid":35365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"//摩連奴決定收起山齊士換入拉舒福特，山齊士被調離場後，先與主帥摩連奴及一眾職球員擊掌，並不見任何不悅之情。//<br />\n<br />\n//山齊士在賽後恭賀球隊獲勝，並沒有露出任何不悅之情//<br />\n<br />\n看圖作文之餘仲要帶晒頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc69db0d9bef5a9516a73dd855185f56c1c23a5d","tid":804510,"uid":34419,"like":0,